# Project Context – AI Platform Engine (APE)

> Engineering standards, architecture, layering, and implementation rules live in `architecture.mdc`.
> This document defines the product vision and scope; that one defines how we build it.

# 📌 Overview

AI Platform Engine (APE) is a production-grade, modular AI Platform designed to integrate with enterprise applications as an independent, self-hosted microservice.

Rather than building AI capabilities directly into business applications, APE provides reusable AI infrastructure through well-defined APIs.

Each customer deploys their own APE instance alongside their application, with complete ownership of their infrastructure, data, models, and configurations.

Typical deployments include:

* Document Management Systems (DMS)
* Tax Audit Systems
* ERP Systems
* HRMS
* Legal Platforms
* Financial Research Platforms
* Internal Enterprise Knowledge Bases

The platform is completely domain-agnostic. It does not contain business-specific logic and can be reused across different industries.

