# 🏗️ Architecture Principles

Every implementation should follow these principles (see `architecture.mdc` for how each is enforced):

* Modular Architecture
* Provider Abstraction
* Configuration-Driven Design
* Separation of Concerns
* Dependency Injection
* Project-Scoped Isolation
* Version Everything
* Background Processing
* Observability First
* Security by Design
* Scalability
* Testability
* Reusability

Business applications should never depend directly on AI vendors or AI infrastructure.

