# 🧩 Core Platform Capabilities

The platform provides reusable, Project-scoped services.

## Project Management

* Projects (central entity)
* Workspaces & Collections
* Members & Access Control
* Per-Project Configuration
* Metadata & Versioning

---

## Connectors (Data Sources)

A first-class, pluggable framework for bringing data into a Project.

* File Upload
* SQL / API / Website
* SharePoint / Google Drive / S3
* Incremental Sync & Scheduling
* Connector Health & Status

---

## Storage

A first-class abstraction for persisting raw files and artifacts.

* Object Storage Abstraction
* Raw File Persistence
* S3 / MinIO / Local backends
* Retention & Lifecycle

---

## Document Intelligence

* Parsing
* OCR
* Metadata Extraction
* Content Normalization

---

## Knowledge Processing

Platform capabilities (not a single module):

* Chunking — **`modules/knowledge/`** — structure-aware, multilingual-ready pipeline (auto strategy, token-based config, ADR-010)
* Optional OCR — **`OCRProvider`** (PaddleOCR optional; disabled by default). **Bangla OCR not supported in Phase 1** — see `docs/features/multilingual_support.md`
* Embeddings, indexing, vector storage — **`modules/retrieval/`**
* Hybrid search and reranking — **`modules/retrieval/`** (ADR-007/009)

