## Known Phase 1 limitations

| Limitation | Impact | Workaround / future |
| ---------- | ------ | ------------------- |
| **Bangla OCR** | Scanned or custom-font Bangla PDFs cannot be reliably OCR'd. PaddleOCR 3.7 has no stock `bn` models; `ocr_lang=bn` fails; default English OCR misreads Bengali script | Use PDFs with valid Unicode Bengali text layer, `.txt`/`.docx`, or wait for Bengali-capable `OCRProvider` (Tesseract, cloud, custom Paddle model) |
| **Verified-key cache TTL** | Revoked keys may succeed for up to cache TTL (30–60s) | Accept for Phase 1; domain events invalidate on revoke/org disable; shorten TTL or disable cache if stricter revocation is required |
| Stale `parsing` after worker crash | Document stuck until manual reprocess | Call `POST .../reprocess` |

Canonical detail: `docs/features/multilingual_support.md` (Bangla OCR section), ADR-010/011.

