# 🔑 Guiding Principles

Every architectural decision should maximize:

* Learning Value
* Reusability
* Provider Independence
* Deployability
* Data Isolation
* Production Readiness
* Scalability
* Maintainability
* Observability
* Security
* Cost Transparency
* Engineering Quality

The objective is not to build another chatbot or a single RAG application.

The objective is to build a deployable AI Platform that can be integrated into enterprise systems as reusable AI infrastructure.
